{
  "name": "RPlog_A_Smuggler_Walks_Into_a_Bar_Part_3",
  "title": "A Smuggler Walks Into a Bar (Part 3)",
  "summary": "Pursued by fast Imperial interceptors, the smuggler Jaspar pushes his aging freighter to its limits while the pirate Vane and the Twi'lek mechanic Ka man the guns in a desperate running dogfight. Jaspar barks shield-angling instructions as the trio coordinates fore-and-aft deflectors and turret fire against the swarming TIEs. Ka, despite professing terrible aim without a targeting computer, scores a clean kill on one fighter, and Vane whoops encouragement from the turret even as a TIE bolt blows a console beside Jaspar. With both interceptors finally destroyed and the area scanning clear, the elated crew powers down, Jaspar tossing Vane a fire extinguisher to deal with the smoking damage. Vane keeps a blaster pressed to Jaspar's cheek long enough to steer him to lightspeed before holstering it, and Jaspar pitches the beginning of a mutually beneficial partnership as the pirates disperse toward the cargo hold.",
